PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781395391
OL,3,CUnited States kick off home World Cup
OL,4,Ccampaign with 4-1 win over Paraguay
OL,6,FThe US managed only three goals
OL,7,Fcombined in its four matches at the
OL,8,FQatar World Cup four years ago, and it
OL,9,Fhad never scored more than three in a
OL,10,FWorld Cup match.
OL,12,FBut the Americans were a team
OL,13,Ftransformed while playing in new coach
OL,14,FMauricio Pochettino's more creative
OL,15,Fsystem in front of a passionate, star-
OL,16,Fstudded Los Angeles crowd of 70,492.
OL,18,FParaguay, the co-host's first opponent
OL,19,Fin the group stage, were the lowest-
OL,20,Franked team in Group D and had not
OL,21,Fplayed at a World Cup for 16 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
