PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781395391
OL,3,CUnited States kick off home World Cup
OL,4,Ccampaign with 4-1 win over Paraguay
OL,6,FThe US have advanced to the knockout
OL,7,Fround in four of the last six World
OL,8,FCups they have played, but have yet to
OL,9,Fget past the quarter-finals.
OL,11,FEntering this tournament ranked 17th
OL,12,Fby FIFA, they hope that matches on
OL,13,Ftheir home soil could lead to a World
OL,14,FCup breakthrough.
OL,16,FThe US team's home opener in the World
OL,17,FCup brought tens of thousands of fans
OL,18,Fto the SoFi Stadium, a multi-billion-
OL,19,Fdollar venue home to the NFL's LA Rams
OL,20,Fand LA Chargers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
