PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781395391
OL,3,CUnited States kick off home World Cup
OL,4,Ccampaign with 4-1 win over Paraguay
OL,6,FBefore kick-off, an opening ceremony
OL,7,Ftook place as part of a celebration
OL,8,Fspanning across two days and all three
OL,9,Fhost nations.
OL,11,FThe US ceremony saw high-energy
OL,12,Fperformances from the likes of pop
OL,13,Fstar Katy Perry and rapper Future.
OL,15,FThere was also a star-studded audience
OL,16,Fin attendance, with Tom Cruise, Brad
OL,17,FPitt, Paris Hilton and David Beckham
OL,18,Famong the celebrities watching on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
