PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781395391
OL,3,CUnited States kick off home World Cup
OL,4,Ccampaign with 4-1 win over Paraguay
OL,6,FAlso on Friday (local time), co-host
OL,7,FCanada drew 1-1 in their World Cup
OL,8,Fopener against Bosnia-Herzegovina in
OL,9,FToronto.
OL,11,FAfter a slow start and an early
OL,12,Fsetback for the home team, late
OL,13,Fsubstitute Cyle Larin scored in the
OL,14,F78th minute.
OL,16,FThe Southampton striker, aged 31,
OL,17,Fscored after just two minutes on the
OL,18,Fpitch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
