PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781395391
OL,3,CUnited States kick off home World Cup
OL,4,Ccampaign with 4-1 win over Paraguay
OL,6,FThe result earned Canada their first-
OL,7,Fever FIFA Men's World Cup point after
OL,8,Flosing all six of their previous
OL,9,Fmatches, three in their debut campaign
OL,10,Fin 1986 and three at the 2022 World
OL,11,FCup.
OL,13,FThe match also marked the first-ever
OL,14,Fmen's FIFA World Cup match played on
OL,15,FCanadian soil.
OL,17,FCanada also had its own opening
OL,18,Fceremony, during which Canadian singer-
OL,19,Fsongwriter Alanis Morissette sang the
OL,20,Fnational anthem, and Michael Buble
OL,21,Fperformed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
