OL,3,CUnited States kick off home World Cup
OL,4,Ccampaign with 4-1 win over Paraguay
OL,6,FMexico opened the tournament on
OL,7,FThursday with a 2-0 win over South
OL,8,FAfrica at Mexico City's Azteca Stadium.
